snippet.title: Today’s Subject FIFTY FIFTY at Music Lab [DJ Ashley's Radio' Clock]
snippet.description:
다들 처음엔 긴장한 모습이었지만, 시간이 지나면서 훨씬 더 편안해진 모습을 보여줬는데요!
두 곡의 라이브와 함께 노래도 한 소절, 잔망루피까지!
프로페셔널 한 모습에 귀여운 매력까지!
역시 많은 사랑을 받는데는 다 이유가 있는거 같죠?!

귀여운데 실력은 안귀여워! 
그래서 더 멋진 피프티 피프티의 이야기 들어보세요!

FIFTY FIFTY seemed very nervous at first,
but each member showed their characteristics as time passed!

Along with two live performance, they each sang a part of a song they like, and even showed us a cute facial expression of the character Loopy!
FIFTY FIFTY boasted many of their charms, from their professional sides to cute sides!
It seems that there definately is a reason why they are receiving so much love world wide, right?

They are cute, but their abilities aren't cute!
That's what makes FIFTY FIFTY so outstanding!
Let's take a listen to FIFTY FIFTY's story.
